N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 470.4 - Overpaid unemployment insurance benefits

State Regulations

The Commissioner of Labor shall, as provided for in
section
18
of the

State Finance Law, waive the assessment of interest and late charges on debts
owed which occurred as a result of overpayment of unemployment insurance
benefits. Notes
